  "rules": {
    "rust-source-line-limits": {
      "description": "All Rust source files in the Yew frontend must remain strictly between 25 and 250 lines (inclusive).",
      "pattern": "frontend/src/**/*.rs",
      "check": {
        "type": "regex",
        "value": "^(?:.*\\n){25,250}$",
        "message": "Rust source files in the frontend must be between 25 and 250 lines."
      }
    }
  }
}

# Project Principles

- **Frontend Rust File Size Limit**: All Rust source files in the `frontend/src` directory must be strictly between 25 and 250 lines of code (inclusive). This keeps modules small enough for fast incremental compilation.
- **Vanilla Styling**: All styling lives in `frontend/Assets/app.css` plus shared CSS imported from `shared-frontend` (vendored into `frontend/Assets/shared-assets/styles/` at build time). No CSS-in-Rust, no Tailwind, no UI framework.

# Project Structure

## Frontend (`frontend/`) — Yew + Trunk

- `frontend/src/main.rs`: Crate root. Declares submodules and mounts `App`.
- `frontend/src/app.rs` + `frontend/src/app/{update,view}.rs`: Root `App` component (msg enum, state, and view split).
- `frontend/src/api.rs`, `storage.rs`, `types.rs`: HTTP helpers, local-storage adapters, shared DTOs.
- `frontend/src/i18n.rs` + `frontend/src/i18n/{en,de,es,fr,ja,pt,ru,zh}.rs`: Locale strings.
- `frontend/src/components/`:
  - `header.rs`, `footer.rs` — thin re-exports of `shared_frontend::Header` / `Footer`.
  - `pin.rs` — PIN login view.
  - `event_listener.rs` — global keyboard / focus / online-status wiring.
  - `snake_state.rs` — reducer / hooks for snake state (direction, segments, score, food, gold timer).
  - `snake_logic.rs` — pure tick + collision helpers (used by `snake_game`).
  - `snake_board.rs` — grid renderer.
  - `snake_game.rs` — top-level game component composing board + overlay + dpad + leaderboard.
  - `snake_overlay.rs` — gold-food countdown + game-over overlays.
  - `snake_dpad.rs` — touch / on-screen D-Pad.
  - `snake_leaderboard.rs` — fetches + renders Top 10.

## Backend (`backend/`) — Axum + Tokio

- `backend/src/main.rs`: Wires logging, env, `AppState`, router; binds TCP.
- `backend/src/config.rs`: `AppConfig` wrapping `shared_backend::server::ServerConfig` with Snake-specific extras.
- `backend/src/state.rs`: `AppState` / `AppStateInner` (config, data dir, leaderboard path, active sessions, per-IP rate limiter).
- `backend/src/routes/mod.rs`: Re-exports + shared handlers (`serve_service_worker`, `health_check`, `serve_asset_manifest`, `serve_manifest`).
- `backend/src/routes/pages.rs`: `serve_root` + `serve_login` + redirect validator.
- `backend/src/routes/leaderboard.rs`: `get_leaderboard` + `submit_score` (file-backed JSON).
- `backend/src/routes/auth/mod.rs`: `is_authenticated`, `require_pin`, `rate_limit_middleware`, cookie name.
- `backend/src/routes/auth/verify_pin.rs`: PIN verification, session ID issuance, cookie write.
- `backend/src/routes/auth/pin_required.rs`: Public `/config` + `/pin-required` endpoints.
- `backend/src/routes/auth/logout.rs`: Session invalidation + cookie clear.

## Build / Runtime

- Trunk builds the WASM frontend from `frontend/index.html` and copies `frontend/Assets/` (including the vendored `shared-assets/styles/`) into `frontend/dist/`.
- The backend serves `frontend/dist/` as static fallback and regenerates `asset-manifest.json` and `Assets/manifest.json` at runtime — do not check in either.